[[span class="o"]]**Special Containment Procedures:** The room affected by SCP-4175 has been removed from the attached building and is currently contained in a large, low-value storage vault at Site-17.[[/span]]
**特別収容プロトコル:** SCP-4175の影響を受けた部屋は建物から取り除かれ、現在はサイト-17の大容量低価値収容保管室に収容されています。
